        "text": "Setting up, testing, and deploying a trading strategy requires time and effort. We test trading ideas to avoid wasting resources.",
        "translations": [
            {
                "language": "ES",
                "text": "Configurar, probar e implementar una estrategia de trading requiere tiempo y esfuerzo. Nosotros testeamos ideas de  trading para no desperdiciar recursos.",
                "updated": 1636724590963
            },
            {
                "language": "DE",
                "text": "Das Einrichten, Testen und Umsetzen einer Handelsstrategie erfordert Zeit und Mühe. Wir testen Handelsideen, um die Verschwendung von Ressourcen zu vermeiden.",
                "updated": 1639251612335
            }
        ]
    },
    "paragraphs": [
        {
            "style": "Text",
            "text": "To test a trading idea, we need to formalize it into a hypothesis that:",
